sentences: Jo Privat (15 April 1919 – 3 April 1996) was a French accordionist and composer.
Privat was born at Ménilmontant, Paris.
Privat was born at Ménilmontant, Paris. He played for many years at Balajo, a musette club in Paris where he worked with Django Reinhardt, the Ferret Brothers, Didier Roussin and Patrick Saussois.
He died at Savigny-le-Temple and was cremated on April 12.
